        <item>
            <title>【開箱】PS5 Pro / PlayStation 5 Pro 港版行貨開箱，主機外觀詳細睇 + 同舊機尺寸、重量比較</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/04/ps5-pro-unboxing/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=ps5-pro-unboxing</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/04/ps5-pro-unboxing/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 11:00:36 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[遊戲情報]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[PlayStation 5 Pro]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[PS5 Pro]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1272937</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>PS5 Pro (PlayStation 5 Pro) 將於 2024 年 11 月 7 日正式公開發售。這部最新強化版 PlayStation，將運行 4K 高解像遊戲畫面時，流暢度由 4K 30fps 增至 4K 60fps，大大提升 4K 遊戲體驗。另外 PS5 Pro 引入自家 PSSR 由 AI 驅動的光線追蹤功能，帶來更迫真的遊戲畫面；主機內置儲存亦升級到 2TB。基於廠方限制，今次我們會先同大家開箱，請留意不久之後我們的詳細評測，屆時我們會為大家實際測試遊戲、看看最新 PSSR 光追效果，還有看看主機散熱情況。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272961" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03530-2-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03530-2-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03530-2.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1272986" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03575-387x580.jpg" alt="" width="490" height="735" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03575-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03575.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 490px" /></p><p>在 PS5 Pro 外箱我們已看到主機獨特的中央格柵設計，遊戲機盒背後印有 PS5 Pro 的新增效能，包括：</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272940" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03501-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03501-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03501.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272942" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03505-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03505-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03505-1.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><strong>PlayStation® 光譜超解析度</strong><br />
使用 AI 增強解析度在 4K 電視上獲得超鮮明的影像清晰度，實現超高畫質播放，呈現令人驚嘆的細節。</p><p><strong>主機效能最佳化</strong><br />
透過支援 VRR、60 Hz 和 120 Hz 顯示器，達到更高且更一致的幀率，實現絲滑流暢的遊戲體驗。</p><p><strong>進階光線追蹤</strong><br />
在您探索精彩絕倫的遊戲世界時，透過光線追蹤反射、陰影和高品質全域光照，享受全新層次的寫實體驗。</p><p>僅適用於與 PS5 相比針對 PS5 Pro 進行增強的特定 PS5 遊戲。PS5 Pro 增強功能會因遊戲而異。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272944" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03500-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03500-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03500.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272945" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03503-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03503-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03503.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲今次我們借來主機盒面印有「無光碟版主機」，代表如果想要玩光碟版遊戲，就需要另購光碟機。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272946" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03506-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03506-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03506.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲盒外亦有註明盒內的內容物</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272947" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03510-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03510-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03510.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲打開盒後，可即時看到所有配件，包括電源線、USB 充電線、HDMI 線、水平式支架、DualSense 無線控制器等。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272960" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03511-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03511-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03511-1.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲下方就是 PS5 Pro 本體以及印刷物</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272949" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03513-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03513-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03513.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272957" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03525-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03525-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03525.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272956" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03530-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03530-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03530-1.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272953" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03531-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03531-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03531.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲另外為安全起見，廠方強烈建議用户在直立擺放時，配合另購的直立支架使用。圖中顯示的直立支架為另購產品。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272978" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03582-387x580.jpg" alt="" width="387" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03582-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03582.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 387px" /></p><p>今次 PS5 Pro 設計上最為獨特就是它的「百葉簾式」中央飾板，它為主機散熱帶來更好效果。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272971" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03572-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03572-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03572.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272962" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03537-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03537-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03537.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1272963" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03541-387x580.jpg" alt="" width="490" height="735" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03541-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03541.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 490px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272965" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03547-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03547-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03547.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1272972" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03574-387x580.jpg" alt="" width="490" height="735" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03574-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03574.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 490px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1272988" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03545-387x580.jpg" alt="" width="490" height="735" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03545-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03545.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 490px" /></p><p>再細看遊戲主機，你可發現它的體積非常細小，比起 PS5 最原始的第一個版本（非 Slim 版）要瘦得多。實際量度的重量只為 3.056kg，比起原始版 PS5 的 4.482kg 輕上許多。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272966" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03563-387x580.jpg" alt="" width="387" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03563-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03563.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 387px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272967" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03566-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03566-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03566.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272995" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03606-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03606-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03606-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲PS5 Pro 主機重量約為 3.056kg</p><p>看兩部機的側面，全新 PS5 Pro 主機也比較瘦。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272968" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03570-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03570-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03570.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>看看 PS5 Pro 的燈光效果，整體氣氛與早前的 PS5 Slim 版相若，即使在瘦身的主機機身中，仍保留了特色的線條燈光氛圍。燈光映照到外圍的保護蓋上，型式兩種燈光效果。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1272970" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03587-387x580.jpg" alt="" width="490" height="735" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03587-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03587.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 490px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1272979" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03584-387x580.jpg" alt="" width="490" height="735" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03584-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03584.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 490px" /></p><h2>影片：PlayStation 5 Pro 機身燈光實試</h2><div style="padding: 75% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="PS5 PRO 機身燈光" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/1026105599?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script></p><p>主機正面全部改成 USB Type-C 插口，共有 2 個。這也迎合好多 PS5 配件，例如無線耳機、第三方手掣都用上 USB 插頭的特點。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1272974 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024110455405-694x518.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="518" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024110455405-694x518.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024110455405.jpg 1205w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272976" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03579-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03579-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03579.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>PS5 Pro 機身背後可看到有更大比例的散熱口。提供 HDMI、LAN、支援 10Gbps 傳輸速度的 USB Type-A x2 插口、電源插口以及防盜線插口。PS5 Pro 同樣設有增設 SSD 的插槽，由於廠方限制，我們留待下次評測文章繼續為大家介紹。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1272982" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03562-387x580.jpg" alt="" width="490" height="735" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03562-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03562.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 490px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272985" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03561-387x580.jpg" alt="" width="387" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03561-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03561.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 387px" /></p><p>根據廠商要求，今日為大家先做了開箱，我們也跟返規矩。真正 PS5 Pro 主機遊戲體驗、畫面實測將會在不久之後的評測文章中刊出，敬請留意！最後再同大家介紹返 PS5 Pro 的詳細特點。</p><p>今次 PS5 Pro 強化版遊戲主機增加硬件效能，無論在圖像清晰度、畫面流暢度還是硬體性能方面都取得了顯著提升。PS5 Pro 配備了 67% 更多的運算單元（Compute Units），以及 28% 更快的記憶體速度，整體效能提升使遊戲渲染速度高達 45%。再加上進階的光線追蹤技術，讓畫面中的光影反射與折射更加細緻，光線速度更是提升了 2 至 3 倍，帶來真實而逼真的視覺效果。另外透過 PlayStation Spectral Super Resolution（PSSR）由 AI 驅動的超解像度技術，透過機器學習來增強畫質，讓 4K 電視上的畫面達到超高清晰度，呈現遊戲中的精緻細節。</p><h2>流暢的遊戲體驗</h2><p>PS5 Pro 支援 60Hz 和 120Hz 顯示器，提供穩定且高效的幀率，適合各類型遊戲的流暢操作，尤其在快速動作和射擊遊戲中更顯優勢。這項特性還相容於具光線追蹤功能的遊戲，使玩家可以在 4K 電視上以 60fps 或最高 120fps 體驗逼真的視覺和流暢的操作。</p><p>PS5 Pro 配備 2TB SSD，大幅擴充了遊戲儲存空間，讓玩家可以輕鬆下載並隨時啟動喜愛的遊戲。主機支援最新的 Wi-Fi 7 無線技術，為線上遊玩提供更高的頻寬和低延遲的連線體驗，在多人連線遊戲中享受穩定的網路環境，減少延遲問題。</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
